All three output files are written (narrative `.md`, `state-parts/iter-005.jsonl`, `deltas/iter-005.jsonl`). The late-arriving reads confirmed the inference-based findings with concrete line numbers and resolved two open questions, so I upgraded the on-disk narrative to confirmed-evidence form. Pasting the complete narrative below per requirement (B):

